race.description: Gorski Hardox Tough Tippers 5Th Grade F
race.comment: SWING BY (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (16.68) last time out at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of four starts. Sure to be about the mark. FLEETWOOD ODIN (2) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 3 lengths (18.64) at this track. Capable of going close again. MR. MARVELLOUS (4) has won at this course and distance, should be thereabouts.
